{
  "stem": "14060.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two sisters, unfortunately, died before the war, one in 1930-- I didn't even know her-- apparently from some food poisoning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the other sister in-- her name was Sarah Holzer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She died in 1935, apparently of some cancer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember her very clearly because my uncle, the doctor, the Weiler uncle, was very active in taking her to specialists in Vienna, which was known to be an important medical center.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even so, we had hospitals and doctors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But obviously, like today, in bigger cities, the care is better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was, in 1935, '36, I remember standing at the window when they brought her with an ambulance back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Probably by that time, they knew there was nothing to be done.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these are sort of small matters which clearly stick in one's mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now the history of our family is basically as I described it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then is more the contemporary part of it, which I can remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father's occupation, having had all the educational background, was a merchant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Before he got married-- he got married at a late station, when he was 31 years old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was customary in our part of the world that you didn't get married unless you had a living to support your wife and family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I suppose in some circles today, it's different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "However, let it be as it may.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- My father's first business and main business was being a wine exporter, because that area was very much a wine-growing district.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And very successfully, he conducted that business right up till the end of the First World War, when suddenly, overnight, the Austro-Hungarian monarchy broke up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And duties were imposed between the previous empire, like Hungary and Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
